  "html": "<h1>Cloud-Native Applications</h1>\n<div class=\"blocks\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">### OntologyBlock</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"cloud-native-applications-ontology\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-2-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:class:: mv:Cloud-NativeApplications</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:physicality:: ConceptualEntity</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">owl:role:: Concept</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Scalability**: Applications handle increased workloads without requiring software redesign or rewriting.[2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Resilience**: Loosely coupled services ensure that individual component failures do not cascade across the system.[2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-3\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Observability**: Built-in monitoring and logging capabilities provide visibility into system behaviour and performance.[1][2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-4\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Manageability**: Automated lifecycle management from development through production reduces operational toil.[2]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-5\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Agility**: Shorter application lifecycles and frequent, predictable deployments enable rapid incorporation of user feedback.[4]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-6\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">CNCF published materials and white papers on cloud-native technologies</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-7\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Industry reports from analyst firms specialising in cloud infrastructure</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-8\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Technical documentation from Kubernetes and container ecosystem projects</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-9\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">DevOps and software engineering literature addressing microservices patterns</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-10\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">British contributions and implementations</div>\n<div class=\"block-children\">\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-0\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Research institutions and programmes</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-1\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">Industry adoption</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-1-2\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">North England innovation (where relevant)</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-11\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Created**: 2025-11-11</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-12\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Source**: Gartner Emerging Technology Analysis</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-13\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Category**: Infrastructure &amp; Cloud</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\" data-id=\"block-0-14\">\n<div class=\"block-content\">**Status**: Emerging Technology</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
